{"tid":1511982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 食宵夜心得，想食嘅全部入一入","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:25:22.000Z","uid":62025,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"85dd07ded91f9e668a8442f091bbf24b4aaa9268","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"次次食宵夜都有唔少手足大意被狗咬<br />\n有見及此<br />\n小妹決定分享小小心得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動大原則：不被捕</span><br />\n唔好因為貪方便而著拖鞋，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定要著波鞋</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n裝束<br />\n根據行動而定<br />\n1.純花生友(如果完全唔支持阿蛇/唔叫口號)<br />\n口罩＋CAP帽因人而異，現場一般有記者，如果唔想上鏡，最好戴埋<br />\n2.啦啦隊/燈光師<br />\n口罩+CAP帽必備，最好用面巾取代口罩順便遮埋耳仔<br />\n目測現場有唔少人會影相，一個唔好彩俾狗咬到，又做到證據就唔係咁好<br />\n如果真係咁唔好彩／走緊果時好驚，是但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搵個暗位掉左燈</span></strong></span>，口罩／面巾＋CAP帽佢穩陣啲<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">消息</span></strong><br />\n一定要時刻留意TG各大Group，如Scout，街坊group,612reminder等等<br />\n幾時要走? 以今日深水埗為例<br />\nScout:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2306 深水埗警署有一架白色大旅遊巴出左警署，往荔枝角道行駛<br />\n2344 5豬 5EU 深旺道 standby<br />\n0009 大埔道南昌街 3馬3沖3豬<br />\n0015 汝洲街楓樹街交界7車<br />\n0016 欽州街 出左6豬籠2EU<br />\n</span><br />\n見到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2344</span>果條消息果時，如果唔熟地型，麻煩拎手機google下啲狗離你幾遠，諗定逃生路線<br />\n如果係女仕／對腳力冇乜信心／唔想進行高強度賽跑，基本上已經可以走<br />\n而家啲狗，目的係咬人，唔係驅散<br />\n基本上如果你諗住<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到狗落車先跑，就已經太遲</span></strong><br />\n因為街坊由９點開始落街食宵夜，俾足３個鐘佢地<br />\n你估佢地仲會咁好心，留生路俾你走？<br />\n宵夜／糖水可以日日食，如果貪好玩留多陣而被狗咬真係好唔抵。<br />\n有哨兵幫曬你手，唔好浪費人地心機。<br />\n亦都唔好怕做散水撚，如果食宵夜都要打陣地戰，咁真係好撚笨柒。<br />\n收到TG可靠消息就同埋街坊傳出去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0724d64d3e0d015a229fd47134d5554490c7cfde","tid":1511982,"uid":55128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=5f8c7343\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=368c26ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=c18ccb2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"183b19b1b98668458ded0aec7b26b78d534812ae","tid":1511982,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家, 憎黑警既投個票:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（公投）十一我有個大膽想法，不如直頭搞個臨時政府出黎？ (修訂版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511951</a>"},{"pid":"7b250a9e077cbf0a7277b414ae771d06852ed175","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"１／１０"},{"pid":"d832b853c7e19b7b28ba2ce1dca4f83d888b8aa2","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"２／１０"},{"pid":"db0fca0d5df410f74139f88e4ff283d190756905","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"３／１０"},{"pid":"a3ddaab0be579810eee170d2473c56079a47fefe","tid":1511982,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b49783ee68d95d