":1511982,"uid":4739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"忌戀戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:30:02.000Z","msg":"係阿，忌輕敵<br />\n就算果到係你樓下行兩分鐘就到<br />\n你見到狗果一刻佢地已經ＳＥＴ好曬包圍網<br />\n其實真係好危險，一定要睇住TG消息<br />\n求下大家，唔好因為自己屋企附近就輕敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b4414aee9d9418082e061bbd312d87b81dbf2f","tid":1511982,"uid":66978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38959b8e7ec07dd45ca4a6daa5baf33fa5091b64","tid":1511982,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:31:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17c32a597b0037e1caccdf702498947b33414f75","tid":1511982,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ffa63a44ee112b29a672ebfc4068d289d67ad65","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"而家已經唔會用防暴長盾推<br />\n因為啲狗俾手足撚過幾次，而家真係想捉人祭旗<br />\n<br />\n同埋剛剛都試過幾次，有時有啲藍屍想撩交打／高空擲物<br />\n成班手足即刻就沖埋去起哄<br />\n但完全冇人留意路面，如果呢個時候即刻有狗由嘉頓＋荔枝角道＋內街出黎，咁有十個手足以前俾狗咬真係唔出意<br />\n<br />\n求下大家要保持警覺，覺得危險／開始收到風有狗行動就散<br />\n糖水日日食，狗屋一次都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a0b75676d28cf445d7c266b0f86285654cfece","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"要學識幾時開始危險＋要走"},{"pid":"fe724e825b412f48c9c5f3e7db3ec84df4e815e5","tid":1511982,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:41:13.000Z","msg":"不被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宵夜先長食長有"},{"pid":"7c3c04b3727dfab9c1abcebd6a07ec153ab65f14","tid":1511982,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"mar係咩部隊<br />\n仲有hki"},{"pid":"9eefffd00d4ce32c20dec50b1776cea8616d9ec8","tid":1511982,"uid":62025,"like":